Hilal Browser: enable transparent macOS chrome surfaces

Makes Hilal top-level macOS windows non-opaque when the Hilal
transparent chrome pref is enabled, then softens the browser chrome,
sidebar, content frame, and new tab page into translucent Tahoe-style
glass surfaces.

